{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 273467, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 52974, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "你不是统治阶级，所以你觉得没意义", "timestamp": 1598007610, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 273471, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 52974, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "中国人的酒bai文化最主要的意义其du实就是礼仪。在古代喝酒其实不是zhi一种娱乐活动，其实是dao在祭祀或者节庆的时候才会有的。一般都是上级奖励下级的时候才会喝酒的。其实也不是非要喝酒，只是在一些场合，为了尊重当家人，并且做到有礼貌，才不得已非要喝酒。", "timestamp": 1598007638, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 273473, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 52974, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "baiduzhidao", "timestamp": 1598007648, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 273475, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 52974, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "检验忠诚度；填补nt群体的精神空虚", "timestamp": 1598007679, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 273476, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 52974, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 现在2020年了，还有什么意义？", "timestamp": 1598007679, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 273479, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 52974, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 现在的酒文化变味太多了…", "timestamp": 1598007762, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 273485, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 52974, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "不喜欢酒桌，也跟我爸讨论过，我爸说和喝酒的人在饭桌上聊天比较活络，不喝酒的人大部分很难熟悉起来和沟通。有时候觉得酒充当一种提升交流效率的催化剂。", "timestamp": 1598007915, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 273488, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 52974, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "我爸也很不喜欢喝酒，但是他觉得在桌上和不喝酒的人很难谈，感觉气氛很难搞热？", "timestamp": 1598007978, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 273500, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 52974, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave: 那为什么  我装出醉醺醺的样子不像喝酒的吗", "timestamp": 1598008093, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 273507, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 52974, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "不喝酒只吃饭会很无聊，而且饭局会结束的很快。喝酒你可以和全桌任何一个人很流畅的互动，但是不喝的话可能一场饭局下来就和自己隔壁的人 说过话。我个人也不喜欢酒局，这特指那种和亲戚在一起，强行要敬酒那种。", "timestamp": 1598008166, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 273512, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 52974, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Eve: 用其他饮料代替 再装醉  和酒有什么不同", "timestamp": 1598008288, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 273530, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 52974, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 我也不知道，我也觉得很神奇", "timestamp": 1598008541, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 273532, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 52974, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 没什么不同，主要是有人喜欢那种微醺的感觉，愿意喝一点酒。而且你装醉干啥....喝酒又不是要把你喝醉了。", "timestamp": 1598008541, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 273537, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 52974, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Eve: 酒精有害  一点不想喝…", "timestamp": 1598008637, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 273539, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 52974, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Eve: 真朋友局肯定是愿意喝一点的，但是现实中是亲戚/工作应酬局远远多于自己的局", "timestamp": 1598008648, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 273542, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 52974, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 可能是因为大部分人喝了点酒之后都会变的话多？我之前去见对象家长，一开始有点小尴尬话比较少，然后对象亲戚喝了点酒，顿时话多了，气氛突然变得活跃，然后会谈一些比较私人的事情，别的亲戚就会打哈哈说，你看他又喝多了～之类的，所以可能微醺达到话多和掩饰在理性情况下不会说出的交心话才是本质？", "timestamp": 1598008680, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 274614, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 52974, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave: 你的私人的事情可能成为下一个酒局的谈资。", "timestamp": 1598026410, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 4, "pid": 52974, "reply": 17, "tag": null, "text": "酒文化有什么意义？", "timestamp": 1598007584, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1606782606, "url": "", "vote": {}}}